Tere Bin Episode 07 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 18th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: தை அமாவாசை 2023 - அன்று செய்ய வேண்டிய 5 மிக முக்கிய விசயங்கள் | Thai Amavasai 2023 | Thai Amavasya
snippet.description:
அமாவாசையில் ஆண்கள் கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டிய & பெண்கள் கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டிய 5 விசயங்கள் 
https://youtu.be/WkwBLdcp-58

விரதம், தர்ப்பணம் யார் செய்யலாம் & யார் செய்யக்கூடாது? Amavasai fasting | Amavasya
https://youtu.be/4sDNKWf5Ico

தை அமாவாசை இந்து சமயத்தவர்களுக்கு மிகவும் புனிதமும் சிறப்பானதுமான தினமாகும். தை மாதத்தில் வருகின்ற அமாவாசை தை அமாவாசை விரதம் எனச் சிறப்புப் பெறுகின்றது. 

தமிழ் மாதங்களில் எல்லா மாத அமாவாசை நாட்களுமே சிறப்பானவை என்பதால் தாய், தந்தையரை இழந்தோர் தங்களின் பெற்றோர் மற்றும் மூதாதையரை கருத்தில் நினைத்து அமாவாசை நாட்களில் விரதம் கடைபிடிப்பர். இதை அமாவாசை விரதம் என்பர். 

ஆனால் குறிப்பிட்ட சில மாதங்களில் வரும் அமாவாசை நாட்கள் சிறப்பு வாய்ந்தன. அவற்றில் முக்கிய இடம் வகிப்பது ஆடி அமாவாசை, புரட்டாசி அமாவாசை மற்றும் தை அமாவாசை ஆகியன. தை அமாவாசை அன்று ஆண்டின் பிற அமாவாசை நாட்களில் கடைபிடிக்க இயலாதவர்கள் ஆறு, கடல் போன்ற புனித நீர்நிலைகளில் நீராடி மூதாதையர்களுக்குப் படையல் செய்து திதி செய்வர்.

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

# சிரார்த்தம் 
# திதி 
# amavasai

ஆனால் குறிப்பிட்ட சில மாதங்களில் வரும் அமாவாசை நாட்கள் சிறப்பு வாய்ந்தன. அவற்றில் முக்கிய இடம் வகிப்பது ஆடி அமாவாசை, புரட்டாசி அமாவாசை மற்றும் தை அமாவாசை ஆகியன. தை அமாவாசை அன்று ஆண்டின் பிற அமாவாசை நாட்களில் கடைபிடிக்க இயலாதவர்கள் ஆறு, கடல் போன்ற புனித நீர்நிலைகளில் நீராடி மூதாதையர்களுக்குப் படையல் செய்து திதி செய்வர்.

snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 08 Teaser - 18th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3671 - 18 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3671: Jetha Ki Anghooti
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha performs a prank on Bhide by asking him to search for his gold ring that has fallen from his balcony. He himself goes inside his house as Bhide searches for the gold ring. When Bhide gets to know about the prank, Jetha and Bhide get into a brief amusing quarrel. When Bhide calls Bapuji to take revenge, Bapuji chastises Jetha in retaliation. Jetha explains the true cause of Bhide's call, and Bapuji reprimands both of them. Tapu Sena arrives at Bhide's home and partakes in some delicious Madhavi-made 'poha' and 'sabud dhana'.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3671, 18 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

localized.description:
Episode 3671: Jetha Ki Anghooti
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha performs a prank on Bhide by asking him to search for his gold ring that has fallen from his balcony. He himself goes inside his house as Bhide searches for the gold ring. When Bhide gets to know about the prank, Jetha and Bhide get into a brief amusing quarrel. When Bhide calls Bapuji to take revenge, Bapuji chastises Jetha in retaliation. Jetha explains the true cause of Bhide's call, and Bapuji reprimands both of them. Tapu Sena arrives at Bhide's home and partakes in some delicious Madhavi-made 'poha' and 'sabud dhana'.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3671, 18 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Guests At The Gada House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Throwback
snippet.description:
Episode 1186: Guests At The Gada House 
---------------------------------------------------
Tusshar Kapoor and Vinay Pathak in Gada House - All the members of the Gada Family are surprised to see the star cast of Bajate Raho. Daya, Jethalal, and Bapuji are excited to meet Actors Tusshar Kapoor, Vinay Pathak, and Vishakha. Is there a surprise waiting for Gada Family?

Show Name- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast -  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Shailesh Lodha
Full Episode - 1186
Produced By - Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a6aWvIzLwbDe6FzzowRhMq

snippet.title: षटतिला एकादशी की कथा || shattila ekadashi ki katha || ekadashi vrat katha
snippet.description:
षटतिला एकादशी की कथा || shattila ekadashi ki katha || ekadashi vrat katha
आज 18 जनवरी,2023 को मैं षटतिला एकादशी व्रत कथा का वीडियो प्रस्तुत कर रहा हूँ। षटतिला एकादशी माघ मास कृष्ण पक्ष की एकादशी को आती है।
Today on 18 January,2023 I am presenting the video of shattila ekadashi vrat katha. Shattila ekadashi comes on ekadashi of magh maas krishna pakash. Magh Maas Krishna Paksha Ekadashi is known as shattila ekadashi. Lets watch video of Shattila Ekadashi ki Kahani, Shattila Ekadashi ki Katha, Shattila ekadashi vrat Katha, Shattila ekadashi vrat ki katha, shattila ekadashi pooja. People pray to Lord Vishnu on the auspicious day of Shattila Ekadashi.  In the video of Shattila Ekadashi Katha, One old lady got everything after performing shattila ekadashi vrat and shattila ekadashi puja vidhi. 
Shatila Ekadashi will be celebrated on 18 January 2023, Friday.
in second shattila ekadashi katha, one woodcutter had changed his life by performing shattila ekadashi vrat. He and his wife both followed shattila ekadashi puja vidhi and performed shattila ekadashi vrat and listened shattila ekadashi ki kahani. after that, they became honorable people of their village. 
Jai shri Hari vishnu bhagwan
षटतिला एकादशी 18 जनवरी 2023, शुक्रवार के दिन मनाई जाएगी.
भगवान श्री कृष्णबोले—नृपश्रेष्ठ! सुनो, माघ मास के कृष्णपक्ष की एकादशी का नाम षटतिला एकादशी है, जो सब पापों का नाश करने वाली है।  षटतिला का अर्थ है-  तिल का छह प्रकार से प्रयोग करना  
तिल से  स्नान 
तिल का उबटन लगाये,    षटतिला एकादशी 2023 की कथा ekadashi vrat katha
तिल से होम करे; 
तिल मिलाया हुआ जल पिये, 
तिल का दान करे 
और तिल  का भोजन । 
इस प्रकार छः कामों में तिल का उपयोग करने से यह एकादशी ‘षट्‌तिला’ कहलाती है। श्री हरि विष्णु भगवान जी की पूजा की जाती है। अब तुम षटतिला एकादशी की कथा सुनो, जिसे मुनि श्रेष्ठ पुलस्त्य ने दाल्भ्य जी से कहा था। 
षटतिला एकादशी की कहानी 
#षटतिला #एकादशी #shattilaekadashivratkatha #shattila #ekadashi

snippet.title: Introducing the all-new HomePod | Apple
snippet.description:
A powerful, high-excursion woofer and beamforming tweeters create room-filling sound. HomePod senses its surroundings and automatically adapts audio for where it’s placed. Advanced computational audio, powered by Apple silicon, optimizes acoustic performance. Spatial Audio directs music with great precision, surrounding you in sound. It all comes together for the ultimate home audio experience. 

HomePod also works seamlessly with all your Apple devices. It comes with Siri built in and works as a smart home hub to connect and control your home, privately and securely. Available in Midnight and White.

“GMT (Jamie xx Remix)” by Oliver Sim and Jamie xx https://apple.co/GMT-Remix

Learn more about HomePod: https://apple.co/3iPMmC7

#Apple #HomePod

Spatial Audio works with compatible content in supported apps.
Music streaming services may require a subscription.
Smart home functionality requires a HomeKit- or Matter-enabled accessory. Smart home accessories sold separately.

Welcome to the official Apple YouTube channel. Here you’ll find news about product launches, tutorials, and other great content. Apple’s more than 160,000 employees are dedicated to making the best products on earth, and to leaving the world better than we found it.

snippet.description:
Join us as we witness the thrilling spectacle of Alanganallur Jallikattu, one of India's most famous and traditional bull-taming events. Held annually in the small village of Alanganallur in Tamil Nadu, Jallikattu is a test of strength and courage as participants attempt to tame the wild bulls. This event is steeped in tradition and culture and is a must-see for anyone visiting Tamil Nadu. Don't miss out on the chance to experience the excitement of Jallikattu and the vibrant culture of Tamil Nadu. Watch our video to see the action and taste of this unique event.

Farq Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 17th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3670 - 17 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3670: 50 TV Ki Delivery
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jetha arrives at his store first thing in the morning, he discovers that Bagha has vanished and Nattu Kakka's phone is also not working. They don't pick up when he attempts to call them on the phone. When he tries to phone Bagha, there is no trace of him; however, he discovers Nattu Kaka at the shop. When Bagha finally enters the store, Jetha starts to doubt him. Jetha becomes quiet when Bagha says that he was in the godown. Later, Bawari enters the store.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3670, 17 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

The Pandeys decide to reveal the truth about Bihaan to Thapki and cure him with her help. Watching things get out of hand, Shraddha tortures Bihaan by reminding him of his traumatic past when he was separated from Thapki. Will this make his situation worse?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. snippet.title: Oh Ni Reh Gaya Yaara (Full Video) Harbhajan Mann | Babu Singh Maan | Laddi Gill | New Punjabi Songs
snippet.description:
Subscribe to HM Records : http://bit.ly/HMRecords

“ਉਹ ਨੀ ਰਹਿ ਗਿਆ ਯਾਰਾ” , ਤੁਹਾਡੀ, ਮੇਰੀ ਸਭ ਦੀ ਕਹਾਣੀ ਹੈ। ਆਪਣਿਆਂ ਤੋਂ ਮਿਲੇ ਜ਼ਖਮ ਤੇ ਧੋਖੇ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਨੂੰ ਸਭ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਤਕਲੀਫ਼ ਦਿੰਦੇ ਆ। “ਬਾਬੂ ਸਿੰਘ ਮਾਨ” ਸਾਹਬ ਦੀ ਕਲਮ, ਜ਼ਿੰਦਗੀ ਦੇ ਇਸ ਸੱਚ ਨੂੰ ਬਿਆਨ ਕਰ ਰਹੀ ਹੈ। “ਲਾਡੀ ਗਿੱਲ” ਦਾ ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਪਿਆਰਾ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਤੇ ਸਟਾਲਿਨਵੀਰ ਦਾ ਮਿਹਨਤ ਨਾਲ ਤਿਆਰ ਕੀਤਾ ਇਹ ਵੀਡਿਓ, ਆਸ ਹੈ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਬਹੁਤ ਪਸੰਦ ਆਏਗਾ।

HM Records present "Oh Ni Reh Gaya Yaara", the latest track from the album "My Way: Main Te Mere Geet". Beautifully written by Babu Singh Maan, with fine musical treatment by Laddi Gill and wonderfully visualized by Stalinveer, the song illustrates the trials and tribulations that occur in friendships, and it is sure to strike a chord with any person who has gone through similar experiences.

snippet.title: सनी देओल ने अमृता सिंह को दी 'किस' की सज़ा - Betaab - Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Shammi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

This film is a love story of two youngsters who fall in love despite the status gaps between their families. Sunny, is a young, poor and happy guy who lives with his mother Sumitra in his home-made town farm. Formerly, his father Avenash had been a big businessman, but he went bankrupt. For this reason, he killed himself. Avenash was close friends with Sardar Dinesh Singh Girji who is one of the richest and most powerful men in the city. When Sardar reveals that Avenash has gone bankrupt, he turns his back to him. Sardar has one daughter called Roma. She is spoiled, snobbish and accustomed to having all the people who surround her beneath her. She was Sunny's childhood friend.

Now, Sardar purchases a new horse farm out of the city in the town, which is nearby Sunny's farm. When Sunny accompanies his mother to the train station, he encounters Roma after not seeing her for years. Sunny instantly recognizes her, but Roma doesn't. Consequently, they coincidentally meet each other various times on the farm. They quarrel continually, but soon she realises that he is her childhood friend and they reconstruct their childhood love.

Directed by Rahul Rawail
Written by Javed Akhtar
Produced by Bikram Singh Dahal
Starring - Shammi Kapoor, Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Nirupa Roy, Prem Chopra, Rehana
Cinematography Manmohan Singh
Music by Rahul Dev Burman

यह फिल्म दो युवाओं की प्रेम कहानी है जो अपने परिवारों के बीच स्थिति के अंतर के बावजूद प्यार में पड़ जाते हैं। सनी, एक युवा, गरीब और खुशमिजाज लड़का है जो अपनी मां सुमित्रा के साथ अपने घर के कस्बे के खेत में रहता है। उनके पिता अविनाश पहले बड़े बिजनेसमैन थे, लेकिन उनका दिवालिया हो गया। इसी वजह से उसने अपनी जान दे दी। अवनाश सरदार दिनेश सिंह गिरजी के करीबी दोस्त थे जो शहर के सबसे अमीर और सबसे शक्तिशाली व्यक्तियों में से एक हैं। जब सरदार को पता चलता है कि अविनाश दिवालिया हो गया है, तो वह उसकी ओर पीठ कर लेता है। सरदार की एक बेटी है जिसका नाम रोमा है। वह बिगड़ैल है, दंभी है और अपने आसपास के सभी लोगों को अपने नीचे रखने की आदी है। वह सनी की बचपन की दोस्त थी।

अब, सरदार शहर के बाहर कस्बे में एक नया घोड़ा फार्म खरीदता है, जो सनी के खेत के पास है। जब सनी अपनी मां के साथ ट्रेन स्टेशन जाता है, तो सालों तक रोमा को न देखने के बाद उसका सामना रोमा से होता है। सनी तुरंत उसे पहचान लेती है, लेकिन रोमा नहीं। नतीजतन, वे संयोग से खेत पर कई बार एक-दूसरे से मिलते हैं। वे लगातार झगड़ते हैं, लेकिन जल्द ही उसे पता चलता है कि वह उसका बचपन का दोस्त है और वे अपने बचपन के प्यार का पुनर्निर्माण करते हैं।

संचालन राहुल रवैल ने किया
जावेद अख्तर द्वारा लिखित
बिक्रम सिंह दहल द्वारा निर्मित
कलाकार - शम्मी कपूर, सनी देओल, अमृता सिंह, निरूपा रॉय, प्रेम चोपड़ा, रेहाना
छायांकन मनमोहन सिंह
संगीत राहुल देव बर्मन ने दिया है
